title: x/crypto/ssh: 'no common algorithms'
body:
ssh: handshake failed: ssh: no common algorithm for client to server cipher; client offered:
[aes128-ctr aes192-ctr aes256-ctr aes128-gcm@openssh.com arcfour256 arcfour128]
server offered:
[3des-cbc aes128-cbc aes192-cbc aes256-cbc]


The same mistake:
https://github.com/golang/go/issues/12982
